{"tid":991088,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"華納兄弟影業領導人表示《水行俠》後的DC電影將會更專注在單一作品而非共同宇宙","createTime":"2019-01-22T06:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T15:15:28.000Z","uid":212399,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c38c039499b69b975d4af39af663ac1334801f7b","tid":991088,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"在去年12月上映的DC電影《水行俠》，於全球獲得了相當成功的票房表現，甚至超越了2012年的《黑暗騎士：黎明昇起》，成為了近年最賣座的DC電影作品。<br />\n而在與 The Hollywood Reporter的訪談當中，於一年前升職為華納兄弟影業團隊領導人的陶比艾默瑞奇（Toby Emmerich），透露了在《水行俠》票房上的亮眼表現對往後的DC電影有什麼影響。<br />\n「我感覺我們現在正在轉變方向了，我們正在遵循著DC的腳本走，它和漫威的腳本非常地不同。我們在共同宇宙的聚焦上少很多，我們打算一次處理一部電影，每一部電影都有著自己的公式和創作主體。如果真要形容的話，就是它必須是導演取向的。」艾默瑞奇解釋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=5665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D5665&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=a85fc54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=5665</a>"},{"pid":"1a6a9f1806efde8ab726f5cd7dee1ae3eacebdb8","tid":991088,"uid":74778,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"宜家出黎扮瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a48195a712706112935d94419474b054e9df67","tid":991088,"uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"正義聯盟2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c256f249373e7e887d714e36ba16fda244afdddf","tid":991088,"uid":56720,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c2fc29cde06c9bb4a8b278c208de07f27e29899","tid":991088,"uid":226155,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"導演能力問題"},{"pid":"b25b375623d56c2a7d585d16d0dcd361a32973a2","tid":991088,"uid":31637,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:27:03.000Z","msg":"晒錢請貴價演員雲